data.description: Discover your own private retreat in this captivating bi-level home situated on a sprawling 0.89-acres of land enveloped by lush trees, offering unparalleled privacy and tranquility. With over 2800+ square feet of meticulously crafted living space, including four bedrooms and three full bathrooms, this residence provides the perfect balance of comfort and functionality. Step inside to find a sunlit living area complemented by a cozy fireplace, creating an inviting ambiance for gatherings or quiet moments. The well-appointed kitchen flows seamlessly into a sun-drenched dining area overlooking the expansive backyard, while the lower level recreation/game room offers endless opportunities for entertainment and relaxation. With its serene surroundings and abundance of features, this exceptional property offers a rare opportunity to embrace the joys of suburban living in a tranquil setting. Never worry about losing power, this property comes with a recent generator installed.  Amenities included: boating and fishing, in/outdoor pools, main beach, community center, 6 lakes, parks, basketball, baseball, tennis courts, bar and grill, and more! Call today to schedule your private tour or any questions.
